    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Nova Strike》是一款复古射击游戏，你将被传送到一个遥远的星系，在那里你将面对一波又一波越来越强大的敌人。游戏易于上手，玩法令人着迷，而且每次新游戏都会生成不同的关卡，你可以享受超长的挑战乐趣。每次起飞你都有机会解锁新的升级并改进你的飞船。试着挑战高分纪录！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320280/extras/0eceb4f96e50d37af63517860f2b07d9.poster.avif?t=1764149581\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320280/extras/0eceb4f96e50d37af63517860f2b07d9.webm?t=1764149581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320280/extras/0eceb4f96e50d37af63517860f2b07d9.mp4?t=1764149581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与可怕的敌人战斗</strong></h2><br>尽可能多地摧毁敌舰，同时巧妙地躲避他们的攻击火力。在击败强大的舰队后，你将挑战可怕的头目。你需要观察、学习和预测每个头目的攻击，才有机会击败他们。把自己推到极限，达成完美通关，打破高分纪录。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320280/extras/79cd45501f4b8dacf1faa61e8ac35ee7.poster.avif?t=1764149581\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320280/extras/79cd45501f4b8dacf1faa61e8ac35ee7.webm?t=1764149581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320280/extras/79cd45501f4b8dacf1faa61e8ac35ee7.mp4?t=1764149581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>自定义你的武器搭载</strong></h2><br>你的飞船九种副武器可以解锁和装备，还有大约40种防御和攻击技能。从导弹到手榴弹再到电力场，每一次升级都会带来不同的游戏体验。建造一艘属于你自己风格的飞船，并在每个关卡之间在太空港停留时对其进行完善。每次自定义后，你歼灭敌军舰队的战术都会完全发生变化。合理选择，找到适合你的游戏风格的最佳配置。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320280/extras/0fccab37d4b619e386efda118908a302.poster.avif?t=1764149581\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320280/extras/0fccab37d4b619e386efda118908a302.webm?t=1764149581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320280/extras/0fccab37d4b619e386efda118908a302.mp4?t=1764149581\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>每一次游戏都截然不同</strong></h2><br>玩了又玩：每一次游戏结束都是新冒险的开始。使用你每次通关所获得的持续点数，解锁新的武器和技能，然后开始新的游戏，探索新的程序生成地图。在一次次尝试后变得更强，直到你有能力对抗最后的头目，拯救星系！</p>",
